title: For Sale:  Norinco Ak Hunter series 2 (AK47 disguised as a deer rifle) with accessories.
postcontent:
This Norinco AK Hunter is a "2nd series" with the blonde wood and fixed sights over the receiver. Made in the famed circle 386 factory, this milled AK has a chrome lined 20" barrel for superior accuracy. Very few of these AK's were imported and there will never be more coming in. 

They are wonderful "sleeper" rifles in that to the antis they look like grandpa's hunting rifle, but you can slap in a 30 round mag or a drum when needed, and have the effectiveness and firepower of an AK-47. They are also the platform of choice for folks looking to build an authentic looking Galil clone firing the more economical 7.62x39 round. 

Some handling marks but internally in great shape. This would make an excellent deer gun, truck gun or SHTF weapon. However it is also one that is likely to increase in value over the years.
